app_description: Global pioneering technology RRT Real time ReWrite Translate strikes a perfect balance between the demands for translation speed and accuracy in simultaneous interpretation. It makes simultaneous interpretation possible on a mobile app! Key Features Instant translation in over 15 languages: Japanese Chinese English Spanish German French Italian Russian Korean Thai Czech Indonesian Cantonese Indonesian Vietnamese Automatically detects the languages spoken by both parties Automatically archives conversations and translation content Female or male voice for simultaneous interpretation. Outstanding Advantages of RRT Function Felo s RRT function is a world first utilizing the latest AI technology to achieve a dual breakthrough in fast translation and high accuracy. By ingeniously combining two translation processes and considering text styles and contexts it provides you with more precise and expressive translation results. Versatile Applications Whether you are engaging in face to face communication during international travel participating in international conferences seminars cross border trade exhibitions or multinational company meetings Felo s RRT function will make your communication smoother and more efficient. Furthermore Felo s real time translation is a powerful tool for learning foreign languages and practicing speaking. Let Felo be your intelligent translation assistant ready to meet your language needs and eliminate language barriers in communication.
